{"tid":1797973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"邊到租到旅遊巴？","createTime":"2019-12-26T00:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-26T10:34:38.000Z","uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3965b6bece5066d511aa0421f579697d88a52b4e","tid":1797973,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:22:46.000Z","msg":"見啲警甴出入都有大巴，遲下攪活動都會考慮下租返部<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請問有無人知係咩公司架？有連聯方法最好</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係想攪咩或攪人公司或大巴，只係想知下價錢先"},{"pid":"4c24241a2a79c4de9e15ed4930e7672caf0669bd","tid":1797973,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:24:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9f3db17e67e8d09675a49248b8adbdb46289591","tid":1797973,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:40:30.000Z","msg":"好想知好想知<br />\n新年去bbq想租車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775588bd1d78abdc88536e6e092d694b43f6b93c","tid":1797973,"uid":167345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T00:46:02.000Z","msg":"用 JoJo bus或強記（<a href=\"http://www.kktourshk.com/）一般來說旅遊巴是以目的地和時間來收費的。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kktourshk.com%2F%EF%BC%89%E4%B8%80%E8%88%AC%E4%BE%86%E8%AA%AA%E6%97%85%E9%81%8A%E5%B7%B4%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%A5%E7%9B%AE%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E5%92%8C%E6%99%82%E9%96%93%E4%BE%86%E6%94%B6%E8%B2%BB%E7%9A%84%E3%80%82&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFGLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=40ccac14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.kktourshk.com/）一般來說旅遊巴是以目的地和時間來收費的。</a> 例如平日 非上下班時段收費會比較平，假日的話收費會比較貴而且難租，要早啲訂。訂車時最好付點按金，因為有時啲老細好討厭的，明明訂左車，然後有另一個人訂單價錢高，就接單貴的，然後話冇車。"},{"pid":"39111d16c3530aa5e3d9bd9de5aba9b6633f7b15","tid":1797973,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T10:34:38.000Z","msg":"好多謝你"}]}